			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Safyre is dating Limmy, and they're meant to be shopping for a suit for him - but he keeps getting sidetracked. They don't have the best couple dynamic - Limmy is immature and prone to (expensive) spontaneous purposes, while Safyre is passive-aggressive, demanding, and has a bit of a mean girl vibe. This is the girlfriend's one-liner." />
